00:23:57.460 --> 00:24:00.160 align:middle line:84%
There are several mysteries
associated with the White

00:24:00.160 --> 00:24:02.050 align:middle line:84%
Horse, and there
are many theories

00:24:02.050 --> 00:24:04.640 align:middle line:90%
as to its significance.

00:24:04.640 --> 00:24:06.710 align:middle line:90%
Harriet Vered is a historian.

00:24:06.710 --> 00:24:08.540 align:middle line:90%
She knows the White Horse well.

00:24:08.540 --> 00:24:13.060 align:middle line:84%
In her opinion, it is above
all a geographical marker.

00:24:13.060 --> 00:24:15.940 align:middle line:10%
>> We're talking about
preliterate people who had no

00:24:15.940 --> 00:24:21.040 align:middle line:10%
maps, no GPS, no
navigational equipment.

00:24:21.040 --> 00:24:23.080 align:middle line:84%
This is the veil
of the White Horse.

00:24:23.080 --> 00:24:25.600 align:middle line:84%
And of course,
from down there you

00:24:25.600 --> 00:24:29.350 align:middle line:84%
