view of the White Horse

00:24:29.350 --> 00:24:31.480 align:middle line:84%
because the White Horse
isn't really supposed

00:24:31.480 --> 00:24:35.140 align:middle line:90%
to be viewed from close.

00:24:35.140 --> 00:24:38.080 align:middle line:84%
>> The horse can in fact be
seen from the whole valley.

00:24:38.080 --> 00:24:41.500 align:middle line:84%
