over 100 meters long

00:24:41.500 --> 00:24:43.870 align:middle line:90%
and 35 meters high.

00:24:43.870 --> 00:24:45.790 align:middle line:84%
The white chalk stands
out so as to make

00:24:45.790 --> 00:24:48.760 align:middle line:90%
the design visible from afar.

00:24:48.760 --> 00:24:51.580 align:middle line:84%
>> Every now and then,
let's say every 10 miles,

00:24:51.580 --> 00:24:54.580 align:middle line:84%
something like that, that
would be a day's journey,

00:24:54.580 --> 00:24:57.670 align:middle line:84%
