sign posts saying,

00:25:01.660 --> 00:25:05.500 align:middle line:84%
this is where you can stop
off and rest, and probably

00:25:05.500 --> 00:25:07.240 align:middle line:90%
pay for it too.

00:25:07.240 --> 00:25:09.820 align:middle line:84%
But you would have to
have somewhere for people

00:25:09.820 --> 00:25:14.230 align:middle line:90%
and animals to stay overnight.

00:25:14.230 --> 00:25:18.235 align:middle line:90%
So it must've been a sign post.

00:25:18.235 --> 00:25:21.416 align:middle line:90%


00:25:21.416 --> 00:25:26.762 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:25:26.762 --> 00:25:33.080 align:middle line:90%


00:25:33.080 --> 00:25:35.690 align:middle line:84%
