00:27:27.182 --> 00:27:30.990 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:27:30.990 --> 00:27:35.290 align:middle line:90%


00:27:35.290 --> 00:27:37.880 align:middle line:84%
>> Geoglyphs are mysterious
