to find the truth

00:27:41.150 --> 00:27:43.730 align:middle line:84%
amongst the different
conflicting theories.

00:27:43.730 --> 00:27:45.500 align:middle line:84%
While some seem to
have been reference

00:27:45.500 --> 00:27:48.080 align:middle line:84%
points for past travelers,
this explanation

00:27:48.080 --> 00:27:50.210 align:middle line:84%
doesn't fit the Nazca
Lines, which are

00:27:50.210 --> 00:27:51.410 align:middle line:90%
hard to see from the ground.

00:27:51.410 --> 00:27:54.910 align:middle line:90%


00:27:54.910 --> 00:27:57.190 align:middle line:84%
However, archaeologists
are interested

00:27:57.190 --> 00:28:01.330 align:middle line:84%
by the special relation of the
