lines to irrigation.

00:28:05.148 --> 00:28:09.116 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:28:09.116 --> 00:28:11.600 align:middle line:90%


00:28:11.600 --> 00:28:13.820 align:middle line:84%
Alex from the
Ministry of Culture

00:28:13.820 --> 00:28:16.397 align:middle line:84%
takes us to visit the
