00:28:16.397 --> 00:28:23.860 align:middle line:90%


00:28:23.860 --> 00:28:28.918 align:middle line:10%
>> The ancient Nazca were
great hydraulic engineers.

00:28:28.918 --> 00:28:32.320 align:middle line:84%
They built irrigation
channels, one

00:28:32.320 --> 00:28:36.155 align:middle line:84%
