00:28:36.155 --> 00:28:36.955 align:middle line:90%
today.

00:28:36.955 --> 00:28:39.860 align:middle line:90%


00:28:39.860 --> 00:28:42.940 align:middle line:84%
>> The Nazca civilization was
in the middle of the desert.

00:28:42.940 --> 00:28:45.190 align:middle line:84%
The balance with
nature was precarious,

00:28:45.190 --> 00:28:48.010 align:middle line:84%
