00:28:48.010 --> 00:28:51.310 align:middle line:84%
Droughts and climate variations
brought about catastrophes

00:28:51.310 --> 00:28:53.276 align:middle line:90%
and famines for the population.

00:28:53.276 --> 00:28:56.540 align:middle line:90%


00:28:56.540 --> 00:28:59.580 align:middle line:84%
The Nazca did everything they
could so as not to depend

00:28:59.580 --> 00:29:01.150 align:middle line:90%
on rare rainfalls.

00:29:01.150 --> 00:29:03.705 align:middle line:84%
Especially, they built
complex irrigation systems.

00:29:03.705 --> 00:29:07.950 align:middle line:90%


00:29:07.950 --> 00:29:10.940 align:middle line:84%
Mastering irrigation allowed
the Nazca civilization

00:29:10.940 --> 00:29:12.980 align:middle line:84%
to develop agriculture
and to have

00:29:12.980 --> 00:29:18.330 align:middle line:84%
an impressively large population
for such a desert environment.

00:29:18.330 --> 00:29:22.630 align:middle line:84%
Thanks to this, thousands of
people lived around the city.

00:29:22.630 --> 00:29:25.930 align:middle line:84%
Their wells, still visible,
are incredible constructions

00:29:25.930 --> 00:29:28.490 align:middle line:84%
as much for their design as
for their way of working.

00:29:28.490 --> 00:29:36.700 align:middle line:90%


00:29:36.700 --> 00:29:40.970 align:middle line:84%
>> It has a spiral shape
which makes access easier,

00:29:40.970 --> 00:29:43.630 align:middle line:84%
which is very useful
for periodic cleaning

00:29:43.630 --> 00:29:46.120 align:middle line:84%
as the villagers have to
work to keep the water clear.

00:29:46.120 --> 00:29:48.910 align:middle line:90%


00:29:48.910 --> 00:29:53.570 align:middle line:84%
