stones that collapse

00:29:56.850 --> 00:29:58.860 align:middle line:84%
and there are branches
which block the passages.

00:29:58.860 --> 00:30:06.120 align:middle line:90%


00:30:06.120 --> 00:30:09.000 align:middle line:84%
>> The spiral shape not only
means that the underground

00:30:09.000 --> 00:30:12.210 align:middle line:84%
channels can be maintained, but
also mean that a lot of people

00:30:12.210 --> 00:30:16.030 align:middle line:84%
can get into work
at the same time.

00:30:16.030 --> 00:30:18.520 align:middle line:84%
According to the partisans
of the water theory,

00:30:18.520 --> 00:30:21.820 align:middle line:84%
some of the marks on the plain
follow the underground network.

00:30:21.820 --> 00:30:25.480 align:middle line:84%
Others mark out
groundwater sites.

00:30:25.480 --> 00:30:28.450 align:middle line:84%
Cults would move around on
these lines calling for rain,

00:30:28.450 --> 00:30:32.176 align:middle line:84%
and leaving offerings to ask
for more favorable climate.

00:30:32.176 --> 00:30:36.160 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:30:36.160 --> 00:30:42.640 align:middle line:90%


00:30:42.640 --> 00:30:45.070 align:middle line:84%
But once again, a
recent study shows

00:30:45.070 --> 00:30:48.500 align:middle line:84%
that most of the signs and
marks are not linked to water.

00:30:48.500 --> 00:30:50.950 align:middle line:84%
While water was vital
to the Nazca culture,

00:30:50.950 --> 00:30:53.430 align:middle line:84%
it was not the main reason
for the creation of the lines.

00:30:53.430 --> 00:31:00.320 align:middle line:90%


00:31:00.320 --> 00:31:04.600 align:middle line:84%
It's incredibly complicated to
try and explain the geoglyphs.

00:31:04.600 --> 00:31:07.420 align:middle line:84%
The marks have remained, but
the memory of their creators

00:31:07.420 --> 00:31:08.530 align:middle line:90%
has faded.

00:31:08.530 --> 00:31:11.500 align:middle line:84%
In the absence of reliable
archaeological data,

00:31:11.500 --> 00:31:15.054 align:middle line:84%
it's difficult to
resolve their mysteries.

00:31:15.054 --> 00:31:18.470 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:31:18.470 --> 00:31:25.790 align:middle line:90%


